Project Title: QE E-Commerce Testing Automation
Description:
This project demonstrates end-to-end QE testing of a sample e-commerce application using multiple tools:

Playwright → Fast, modern UI automation

Cypress → Reliable JS-based UI testing

Selenium → Cross-browser legacy UI automation

Postman → API testing & automation

Features Covered:

Login / Logout

Product search & filter

Add to Cart / Remove from Cart

Checkout flow

API validation (Login, Products, Cart, Checkout)

CI/CD integration (GitHub Actions, Jenkins)

How to Run Tests:

Playwright → npx playwright test

Cypress → npx cypress run

Selenium → mvn test

Postman → newman run Ecommerce.postman_collection.json
